Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Politics v baseball
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03zjmlq
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 24 Oct 1976
Baseball v politics. The World Series final clashes with US presidential hopefuls Carter and Ford TV debate. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less